        {
          "text": "In the general discussion channel, several AI and full-stack engineers introduced themselves and their services, highlighting expertise in areas such as autonomous agents, LLMs, RAG pipelines, voice AI, computer vision, and multimodal systems. Frameworks mentioned included LangChain, AutoGen, CrewAI, LangGraph, and various orchestration tools. One community member raised a question about whether the team is still actively supporting the ElizaOS token, noting that Shaw had removed ElizaOS from his X bio, though no official response was provided in the thread. Brief market commentary suggested optimism, with one user noting conditions were favorable and that a catalyst was all that was needed.",
